name: Stormcatch
description: The Stormcatch token is a cutting-edge cryptocurrency designed to revolutionize robot reputation systems in an increasingly automated world. Built on the Avalanche network, Stormcatch enables autonomous machines to establish, maintain, and evaluate their reputations through secure and transparent transactions. By leveraging blockchain technology, the token facilitates real-time feedback and trust assessments, empowering robots to collaborate more effectively and make informed decisions.
